This is fixed in trunk!
```scala
scala> def printSize[T <% {def size: Int}](in: T) = println(in.size)
printSize: [T](in: T)(implicit view$$1: (T) => AnyRef{def size: Int})Unit

scala> 

scala> printSize(List(1, 2, 3))
3

scala> printSize("caw")
3

scala> printSize(Map(1 -> 2))
1

scala> printSize(Array(1, 2, 3))
3
```
